Nigerian professional footballer and goalkeeper, Maduka Okoye has revealed that he is single and searching. Okoye disclosed this in an interview with Nigerian Info, expressing that he loves his women to be full of melanin and toxic. While answering the interviewer who asked him if he was single and searching because a lot of single ladies were listeners show, he responded, “Yeah, I am single, they can hit me up,” Super Eagles Goalkeeper Wins Sparta Rotterdam’s Player Of The… The Super Eagles goalkeeper further said, “I like every type of women but they have to be melanin, I love my melanin. I like my melanin, I like curly and toxic women.” Note that the 22 years old athlete has become a centre of attention as many Nigerian female fans have tagged him as the most handsome Nigerian football player on social media.